Package code.game.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvanceCritter
    Class containing the advanced critter setter
    BasicCritter
    Class containing the basic critter setter
    CastleTower
    Castle tower extends the tower model class and is a a type of tower available in the game
    Critter
    Main model class of critter getting and setting all the characteristics of critter e.g - Health - Speed - Hit points - Level - Player's reward
    CritterFactory
    Critter's Factory pattern which generates different types of critters based on the parameter passed
    GameData
    Class responsible of updating all the data being manipulated in the game e.g - Player's power - Coins - Balance - Wave no.
    GameMap
    the main class of game's map, performing essential tasks about map acts as an observable
    ImperialTower
    Imperial tower extends the tower model class and is a a type of tower available in the game
    IndustrialTower
    Industrial Tower extends the tower model class and is a a type of tower available in the game
    IntermediateCritter  
    TowerModel
    This class defines the necessary properties of the tower and exposes methods to access and modify the tower objects.
